```plantuml
@startuml hypertrack_live-app-android

actor User
participant "Android App" as App
participant "CognitoClient" as Cognito
participant "BackendClientFactory" as Factory
participant "AbstractBackendProvider" as Backend
participant "HyperTrack SDK" as SDK
participant "Google Maps" as Maps
participant "AWS Cognito" as AWS

User -> App: Launches application
App -> Cognito: checkAuthentication()
Cognito -> AWS: authenticateUser()
AWS --> Cognito: authToken
Cognito --> App: authStatus

User -> App: Request live location sharing
App -> Factory: createBackendProvider()
Factory --> App: BackendProvider instance

App -> Backend: createTrip()
Backend -> SDK: startTracking()
SDK --> Backend: trackingStarted
Backend --> App: tripCreated

App -> Maps: displayLocation()
Maps --> App: mapRendered

User -> App: Share trip (generate invite)
App -> Backend: generateInviteLink()
Backend -> SDK: getTripDetails()
SDK --> Backend: tripData
Backend --> App: inviteLink

User -> App: View shared location
App -> SDK: getLiveLocation()
SDK --> App: locationData
App -> Maps: updateLocation()
Maps --> App: mapUpdated

User -> App: Stop sharing
App -> Backend: completeTrip()
Backend -> SDK: stopTracking()
SDK --> Backend: trackingStopped
Backend --> App: tripCompleted

@enduml
```